Invocation Name: citizen watch
Developer Terms of Use
des:
After enabling this skill, you can quickly start a workout, ask for daily fitness progress, control notifications and music, find your phone and many more, with Alexa right on your wrist. Just tell your Citizen watch:
Ask Citizen Watch to start workout
Ask Citizen Watch to enable Do Not Disturb
Ask Citizen Watch to play music
Ask Citizen Watch to find my phone

This skill is only supported on some Citizen smartwatch models.
